        <li><a href="/docs/delegation/">Command Delegation Chain</a> — robot-to-robot delegation after consent</li>
        <li><a href="/docs/offline/">Offline Operation</a> — offline consent blob usage</li>
        <li><a href="/docs/messages/#type-reference">MessageType 20/21/22</a></li>
      </ul>
    </section>
  </article>
